Start a New Project
→ Project → New.

Add Vector Layer
→ Layer → Add Layer → Add Vector Layer
→ Select:
ne_10m_admin_0_countries.zip.

Save Layer with New CRS
→ Right-click the layer → Export → Save Features As
→ Format: ESRI Shapefile
→ Choose folder location & file name
→ Set CRS: North America Albers Equal Area Conic (EPSG: 102008)
→ Press OK.
→ Deselect the original layer, keep the projected one visible.

Add Raster Layer
→ Layer → Add Layer → Add Raster Layer
→ Select:
MiniScale_(standard)_R17.tif
→ Path:
GIS_Workshop/Practicals/Practical_05/DATA/minisc_gb/minisc_gb/data/RGB_TIF_compressed/MiniScale_(standard)_R17.tif

Set Raster CRS
→ Right-click the raster layer → Properties → CRS
→ Search for British National Grid
→ Select EPSG: 27700
→ Press OK.
